information: CARABUS FH INTERNATIONAL is a human-sized import+export business aiming to provide customers and partners with international products from across France. Located in Thiais, CARABUS FH INTERNATIONAL is specialised in wholesale and retail seafood, namely shellfish, fish and molluscs. In addition to exotic food products, like fruit and spices, we also supply drinks, including wines and spirits. Quality, competitiveness and flexibility are the order of the day to guarantee our partners quality products and service, enabling us to build together solid, long-term relations. We respect our produce which is carefully selected and comes from sustainable fishing. We provide the best possible treatment because we are concerned about our environmental impact. We guarantee we respect environmental standards.
